# =====================================================
# đź“Š Analytics & Metrics
# =====================================================

# Local analytics data
analytics-cache/
metrics-data/


# =====================================================
# đź—„ď¸Ź Databases (local development)
# =====================================================

*.sqlite
*.sqlite3
*.db
*.db-journal


# =====================================================
